# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:322
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Parent` property of an effect sets the initial keyframe "
"values to a parent effect. For example, if many effects all point to the "
"same parent effect, they will inherit all their initial properties, such as "
"font size, font color, and background color for a ``Caption`` effect. In the "
"example of many ``Caption`` effects using the same Parent effect, it is an "
"efficient way to manage a large number of these effects."
msgstr ""
"Eiginleikinn :guilabel:`Parent` áhrifa stillir upphafsgildi lykilramma til "
"foreldraáhrifa. Til dæmis, ef mörg áhrif vísa öll á sama foreldraáhrif, erfa "
"þau öll upphaflegar stillingar eins og leturstærð, leturlit og bakgrunnslit "
"fyrir ``Caption`` áhrif. Í dæminu með mörg ``Caption`` áhrif sem nota sama "
"foreldraáhrif er þetta skilvirk leið til að stjórna miklu magni af þessum "
"áhrifum."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:326
msgid ""
"NOTE: The ``parent`` property for effects should be linked to the **same "
"type** of parent effect, otherwise their default initial values will not "
"match. Also see :ref:`clip_parent_ref`."
msgstr ""
"ATH: Eiginleikinn ``parent`` fyrir áhrif ætti að tengjast **sama tegund** "
"foreldraáhrifa, annars munu sjálfgefnu upphafsgildin ekki passa. Sjá einnig :"
"ref:`clip_parent_ref`."

