msgid "tracking"
msgstr "tracking"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:374
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` Horizontal **line wobble** plus a subtle bottom **skew**. "
"Higher values increase amplitude and skew height."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` Lárétt **línuóstöðugleiki** auk smá neðri **skekkju**. "
"Hærri gildi auka sveifluvídd og skekkjuhæð."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:375
msgid "bleed"
msgstr "bleed"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:375
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Chroma bleed / fringing.** Horizontal chroma shift + blur "
"with a slight desaturation. Gives the “rainbow edge” look."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Litblæðing / fringing.** Lárétt litaskipti + óskýrleiki "
"með smá litleysi. Gefur „regnbogabrún“ útlit."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:376
msgid "softness"
msgstr "softness"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:376
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Luma softness.** Small horizontal blur on Y (approx. 0–2 "
"px). Keep low to retain detail when noise is high."
msgstr ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Mjúkt birtustig.** Lítil lárétt óskýrleiki á Y (um 0–2 "
"px). Haltu lágu til að varðveita smáatriði þegar hávaðinn er mikill."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid "noise"
msgstr "noise"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../effects.rst:377
msgid ""
"``(float, 0–1)`` **Snow, hiss, and dropouts.** Controls grain strength, "
